betterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495383%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchools%20act%20as%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20with%20a%20protocol%20to%20report%20absences%20that%20might%20indicate%20forced%20marriage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2010%20July%202025%2C%20one%20of%20her%20teachers%20noticed%20signs%20of%20the%20impending%20marriage%20and%20called%20Childline.%20Acting%20swiftly%2C%20a%20rescue%20team%20of%20district%20officials%20and%20local%20police%20reached%20her%20home%20and%20intervened%20before%20the%20wedding%20could%20be%20solemnised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20rescued%20a%20day%20before%20the%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sampa%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20rescue%20team%20came%2C%20I%20felt%20relieved%2C%20and%20I%20told%20them%20I%20was%20being%20married%20without%20my%20consent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20rescue%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20first%20to%20the%20One-Stop%20Centre%20in%20Bishramganj%20(which%20provides%20medical%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20psychological%20support%20to%20women%20in%20distress)%20and%20later%20to%20the%20Sonamura%20SC%20Girls%20Hostel.%20Her%20parents%20signed%20an%20undertaking%20before%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%2C%20promising%20to%20delay%20her%20marriage%20so%20that%20she%20could%20continue%20her%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20home%2C%20I%20could%20not%20study%20or%20play%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CHere%20in%20the%20hostel%2C%20I%20get%20three%20meals%20on%20time%2C%20I%20can%20study%2C%20and%20I%20can%20play%20kho%20kho.%20I%20especially%20enjoy%20Bangla.%20Now%20I%20want%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%20when%20I%20grow%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20Sampa%E2%80%99s%20underline%20why%20Mission%20Sankalp%20had%20to%20be%20bold%20and%20u