3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20problems%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20in%20isolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CDrug%20abuse%20can%20be%20both%20a%20cause%20and%20consequence%20of%20early%20marriage%20or%20pregnancy.%20So%20we%20chose%20focus%20over%20fragmentation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20them%2C%20the%20mission%20was%20built%20on%20a%20series%20of%20innovative%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Changing%20mindsets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20battle%20was%20for%20minds.%20Through%20Behaviour%20Change%20Communication%20(BCC)%2C%20Village%20Health%20and%20Nutrition%20Days%20became%20platforms%20for%20discussion.%20Schools%20wove%20the%20issue%20into%20everyday%20lessons%2C%20while%20entire%20communities%20began%20taking%20public%20pledges%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244424%2Fdomestic-abuse-rural-women-empowerment-laxmi-waghmare-cii-inspiring-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20child%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBCC%20is%20an%20approach%20that%20uses%20communication%2C%20dialogue%2C%20and%20community%20activities%20to%20shift%20attitudes%20and%20promote%20healthier%20social%20norms.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCollective%20accountability%20is%20a%20powerful%20tool%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20an%20entire%20village%20promises%20to%20protect%20its%20children%2C%20it%20builds%20a%20moral%20firewall.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Schools%20as%20watchdogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20were%20turned%20into%20early%20warning%20systems.%20Teachers%20and%20students%20were%20trained%20to%20spread%20awareness%20and%20to%20use%20the%201098%20Childline%20number.%20A%20%E2%80%9Csix-day%20absentee%20rule%E2%80%9D%20was%20also%20introduced%20%E2%80%94%20if%20a%20student%2C%20especially%20a%20girl%2C%20missed%20more%20than%20six%20days%20of%20class%2C%20the%20school%20was%20required%20to%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20such%20absences%20revealed%20a%20looming%20or%20completed%20child%20marriage.%20The%20response%20was%20swift%20and%20coordinated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Stronger%20enforcement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tighten%20law%20enforcement%2C%20workshops%20were%20held%20for%20sub-divisional%20magistrates%2C%20police%2C%20and%20child%20protection%20units.%20Roles%20were%20clarified%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act.%20Officials%20were%20reminded%20that%20failing%20to%20act%20could%20invite%20punishment%20under%20POCSO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20a%20girl%20is%20married%2C%20any%20sexual%20activity%20with%20her%20is%20still%20statutory%20rape%20under%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20stresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-2-1756816894.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aggressive%20time%20frame%20is%20set%20to%20eliminate%20child%20marriage%20in%20Sepahijala%20by%202027.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-2-1756816894.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-2-1756816894-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-2-1756816894-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F