%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoices%20that%20change%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20teenage%20pregnancies%2C%20especially%20among%20already-married%20girls%2C%20became%20the%20next%20focus%20for%20Mission%20Sankalp.%20A%20list%20of%20eligible%20couples%20was%20drawn%20up%2C%20and%20they%20were%20counselled%20using%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccafeteria%20approach%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20idea%20that%20puts%20every%20contraceptive%20option%20on%20the%20table%20and%20allows%20couples%20to%20make%20their%20own%20informed%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20officials%20even%20began%20attending%20weddings%20of%20legally%20married%20couples%2C%20handing%20over%20%E2%80%9Cnewlywed%20kits%E2%80%9D%20with%20reproductive%20health%20leaflets%2C%20contraceptive%20samples%2C%20and%20family%20planning%20information.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20a%20simple%20leaflet%20at%20the%20right%20time%20can%20delay%20a%20pregnancy%20and%20change%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20Sankalp%20has%20certified%2010%20villages%20child%20marriage-free.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMission%20Sankalp%20has%20certified%2010%20villages%20child%20marriage-free.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20promises%20into%20progress%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20Mission%20Sankalp%20are%20beginning%20to%20show.%20So%20far%2C%2010%20villages%20have%20earned%20%E2%80%9CAspiring%20Child%20Marriage-Free%E2%80%9D%20certification%20by%20preventing%20all%20cases%20of%20child%20marriage%20for%20six%20months%20straight.%20Villages%20that%20sustain%20this%20for%2012%20and%2024%20months%20move%20into%20higher%20recognition%20categories%2C%20creating%20a%20healthy%20spirit%20of%20competition%20across%20Sepahijala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20certification%20process%20is%20closely%20tracked.%20It%20begins%20with%20the%20Gram%20Pradhan%20submitting%20a%20declaration%20of%20compliance%20to%20the%20Block%20Development%20Officer%20(BDO).%20The%20BDO%20verifies%20the%20claim%20and%20forwards%20it%20to%20the%20Sub-Divisional%20Magistrate%20(SDM)%2C%20who%20then%20places%20it%20before%20the%20sub-divisional%20task%20force.%20If%20approved%2C%20the%20proposal%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20(DM)%20within%20a%20month%2C%20where%20the%20district-level%20task%20force%20conducts%20a%20final%20review%20before%20declaring%20a%20village%20eligible%20for%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20rigour%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20villages%20is%20being%20monitored%20in%20phases%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20certifying%20all%20169%20Gram%20Panchayats%20(GPs)%20and%20Village%20Committees%20(VCs)%20across%20Sepahijala.%20Since%20the%20mission%20began%2C%20more%20than%20100%20children%20have%20already%20been%20rescued%20from%20early%20marriage%2C%20with%20rehabilitation%20support%20underway%20to%20help%20them%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20picture%20is%20also%20shifting%3A%20health%20facilities%20reporting%20zero%20deliveries%20among%20under-18%20girls%20have%20risen%20from%20four%20in%20December%202024%20to%2011%20by%20March%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202027%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20hopes%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriage%20in%20Sepahijala%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20three%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20global%20target%20under%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goal%205.3.%20%E2%80%9CMission%20Sankalp%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20another%20initiative%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20personal.%20It%E2%80%99s%20urgent.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20safeguarding%20our%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Sepahijala%20district%20administration.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756872000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-4-1756816819.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D495335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20happens%20when%20one%20district%20decides%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20its%20daughters%20become%20child%20brides%3F%20In%20Sepahijala%2C%20IAS%20officer%20Siddharth%20Jaiswal%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20already%20saved%20100%20children%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20rallying%20entire%20villages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F495335%2Fmission-sankalp-child-marriage-teen-pregnancy-sepahijala-siddharth-jaiswal-ias%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Manoj%20Kumar%20shared%20fond%20memories%20with%20Big%20B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756871648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123668785%2Ci