%20level%20of%20%26quot%3Bfor%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20Humphrey's%20Executor%2C%20a%201935%20landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20that%20established%20how%20a%20sitting%20US%20president%20cannot%20fire%20officials%20of%20an%20independent%20agency%20based%20on%20policy%20or%20political%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2025%2C%20Trump%20posted%20a%20termination%20letter%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20was%20addressed%20to%20Cook%2C%20calling%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20removal%20from%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20responded%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20purported%20to%20fire%20me%20'for%20cause'%20when%20no%20cause%20exists%20under%20the%20law%2C%20and%20he%20has%20no%20authority%20to%20do%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20Trump%20has%20been%20pressuring%20the%20Fed%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates%20as%20the%20board%20continues%20to%20keep%20rates%20steady.%20The%20president%20has%20resorted%20to%20personal%20attacks%20against%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%2C%20calling%20the%20top%20Fed%20official%20a%20%26quot%3Bstubborn%20MORON.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20closely-watched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-jackson-hole-speech-stock-market-interest-rate-cut-inflation-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremarks%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wyoming%2C%20Powell%20indicated%20that%20the%20Fed%20was%20leaning%20toward%20a%2025-basis-point%20rate%20cut%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flisa-cook-fed-governor-mortgage-fraud-allegations-attorneys-response-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756867732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b79588cfc04e97619c71f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flisa-cook-fed-governor-mortgag