d%20the%20promotion%20of%20organized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-flag-football-critical-to-nfl-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflag%20football%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20smart%20approach%20that%20can%20grow%20local%20fan%20bases%20for%20teams%20while%20activating%20new%20sponsorship%20opportunities%2C%20including%20collaborations%20with%20%26quot%3Blarge%20brands%20the%20NFL%20hopes%20to%20cultivate%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20M.%20Carter%2C%20an%20adjunct%20sports%20business%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Sports%20Business%20Group%2C%20a%20sports%20and%20entertainment%20consulting%20firm.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20seven%20more%20NFL%20clubs%20having%20joined%20the%20program%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20league%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foperations.nfl.com%2Fupdates%2Fthe-game%2Fall-32-teams-officially-part-of-nfl-s-global-markets-program%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enow%20has%20all%2032%20teams%20strategically%20aligned%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20one%20or%20more%20countries.%20Several%20franchises%20already%20participating%20also%20announced%20new%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Seattle%20Seahawks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seahawks.com%2Fnews%2Fseattle-seahawks-continue-international-expansion-efforts-as-part-of-nfl-s-global-markets-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20a%20deal%20with%20TGI%20Sport%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20the%20team's%20strategy%2C%20events%2C%20and%20commercialization%20agency%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20Seahawks%20have%20also%20formed%20international%20partnerships%20with%20companies%2C%20including%20Infront%2C%20Condor%20Airlines%2C%20and%20BDA%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0af7ee3-832c-436e-bb07-de8d2d281a34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeasuring%20success%20beyond%20revenue%3C%2Fstro