a.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20jackfruit%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3)%20Selecting%20a%20sapling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGet%20a%20healthy%20sapling%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20or%20try%20growing%20one%20from%20seed.%20The%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week%2C%20but%20the%20cuttings%20may%20take%20more%20than%20a%20month%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355172%2Fhow-to-grow-jackfruit-at-home-easy-tips-steps-diy-guide-grow-bag-balcony-terrace-lucknow%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20from%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20But%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20gently%20place%20the%20sapling%20in%20the%20prepared%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20roots%20are%20spread%20out.%20Water%20thoroughly%20to%20settle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20time%20for%20planting%20is%20June%20to%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Regular%20care%20and%20monitoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20the%20plant%20whenever%20the%20topsoil%20is%20dry.%20Check%20soil%20moisture%20and%20set%20up%20watering%20schedules.%20Yo